{"tid":125320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再有市民被黑警打鑊  比七警更險惡  打人拉人陷害人  無所不用其極","createTime":"2017-02-18T11:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T04:16:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"919129f025e63bff8ce772291e6721556e859967","tid":125320,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/tRD2So.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FtRD2So.png&h=b8501b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不正常人類研究中心<br />\n4小時 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n黑警又點止七個，喱班幾時先會去坐監？<br />\n暗角七警罪有應得, 大快人心. 不過, 原來惡警黑警不只得七個, 仲有很多很多, 希望全港市民齊來合力, 齊來尋找, 再下一城.<br />\n以下呢段片, 受害人不比曾健超少, 身體和精神上的傷害, 只有過之而無不及. 片中呢班有牌土匪, 比七警更加罪惡, 更加明目張膽, 打人拉人陷害人, 無所不用其極. 希望受害者勇敢再次站出來, 再提出控告, 為自己尋求公道; 更希望有義士律師, 挺身而出, 助受害人一臂之力; 令香港的上空, 烏雲散滅, 清天重現.<br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://fb.com/peoplearenormal/videos/581469262051104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fpeoplearenormal%2Fvideos%2F581469262051104%2F&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr126tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ac6c5abe\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/peoplearenormal/videos/581469262051104/</a>"},{"pid":"4ac0920451412e28dbfa70307a9f06ba0c3ac534","tid":125320,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1401cd87488f0b058341261fa028538194121b0f","tid":125320,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5bae84e8735cd30ccc29835d05bcbf908025d85a","tid":125320,"uid":685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19bbc4cbb0c708619b190020f98bfc533cb96e46","tid":125320,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img s